        r"\begin{equation}" "\n"
        r"\mathcal S_\partial = \begin{pmatrix} \sqrt{1-\betatgl} & "
        r"\sqrt{\betatgl} \\ -\sqrt{\betatgl} & \sqrt{1-\betatgl} "
        r"\end{pmatrix} = e^{\thetaM G}, \qquad G = \begin{pmatrix} 0 & 1 \\ "
        r"-1 & 0 \end{pmatrix}," "\n"
        r"\end{equation}" "\n"
        r"with $\mathrm{Spec}(\mathcal S_\partial) = \{e^{+i\thetaM}, "
